    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home! It's been such a fantastic car\u2014super reliable and still feels great on the road. It\u2019s in really nice shape, well-loved, and totally ready for many more adventures. If you\u2019re looking for a solid, dependable set of wheels that won\u2019t let you down, this is definitely the one! I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted E46 M3 powered by the legendary S54B32 atmospheric inline-six. This unit features a recently overhauled Double VANOS system and a documented valve adjustment, ensuring the individual throttle bodies deliver linear power up to the 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis is reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and retains its communicative steering rack and MacPherson/multi-link suspension geometry. Power is sent through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. While the exterior displays minor cosmetic patina, the drivetrain and underpinnings are robust, making this a prime candidate for a driver-centric collection.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Clean title. Well-maintained. Mechanically sound. Ready to drive.",
