    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained sedan in a sophisticated Graphite Metallic finish. This vehicle has been driven with care and remains in solid, reliable condition. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss luster, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch, typical for a well-loved car of this age. Inside, the cabin is a testament to cleanliness; the black leather upholstery is free of tears, though there is light creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. All interior electronics, including the premium sound system, navigation, and heated seats, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is excellent. It features a complete service log, with the most recent synthetic oil change and filter replacement performed just 500 miles ago. The transmission shifts smoothly, and the suspension remains firm and quiet. The tires are matching all-seasons with roughly 70% tread life remaining, and the brake rotors show no signs of warping. This is a turnkey vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
